{
  "stem": "4967.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Germans were not satisfied with the finding of the White Russians, the Ukrainians and Lithuanians, because they knew exactly how many children are in the ghetto and how many people don't work.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we-- the Jewish people were registered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were naive people in those days, at the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they send in German troops.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- first of all, in the morning, the people had to go out of the ghetto to work outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were allowed to go out to work under military guard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the Germans came inside the ghetto and went from house to house to pick up, according to their estimation, how many women are not working, how many children are in the ghetto, and how many sick people may be in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came to our block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We stayed in a block, a three story block of flats or apartments, which the Russians built for the workers in nearby factories.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as they came into our block-- block of flats, our apartment, we were hiding under the staircase, and they find us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they told us to go outside, to stay in the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we came out, and we find some more children standing already there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they told us to march behind a certain officer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went from one flat to another flat, because there were no locks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it's made specially.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Jewish people designed inside it, they can go through the complete apartment building, right through, and the doors were never closed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In case you have to run out of fire or emergency or similar things as happening now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we walked through one flat and another flat and picking up children, women, sick people.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
